{"type":"FeatureCollection","features":[{"type":"Feature","geometry":{"type":"GeometryCollection","geometries":[{"type":"Point","coordinates":[146.01615645493774,-38.19021392853462]},{"type":"Polygon","coordinates":[[[146.0112641056897,-38.18635186054714],[146.00890376176284,-38.190365815099995],[146.0207913121168,-38.1940759965221],[146.02340914811265,-38.190028516508114],[146.0112641056897,-38.18635186054714]]]}]},"properties":{"feedType":"warning","cap":{"category":"CBRNE","event":"Chemical Hazard","eventCode":"chemical","urgency":"Expected","severity":"Minor","certainty":"Unknown","contact":"lily.watson-jones@justice.vic.gov.au","senderName":"Country Fire Authority","responseType":"Monitor"},"sourceOrg":"EMV","sourceId":"42010","sourceFeed":"cop-cap","sourceTitle":"Advice","id":"42010","category1":"Advice","category2":"CBRNE","status":"Minor","name":"Advice","action":"Stay Informed","statewide":"N","location":"Darnum","created":"2026-06-20T09:57:02+10:00","updated":"2026-06-20T09:57:01+10:00","webHeadline":null,"webBody":"<div style=\"margin-bottom:20px\">This <b>Advice</b> message is being issued for <span title=\"warning_locality\" class=\"param\" contenteditable=\"false\">Darnum</span>.&nbsp;<div><ul><li>There are hazardous&nbsp;<span class=\"editable editable-click editable-unsaved\" data-type=\"select\" data-emptytext=\"[gas/material/liquid/solid/fumes]\" data-value=\"4\" contenteditable=\"false\" style=\"display: inline;\" data-source=\"{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;gas&quot;,&quot;1&quot;:&quot;material&quot;,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;liquid&quot;,&quot;3&quot;:&quot;solid&quot;,&quot;4&quot;:&quot;fumes&quot;}\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">fumes</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"editable editable-click editable-unsaved\" data-type=\"select\" data-emptytext=\"[in/at/on]\" data-value=\"2\" contenteditable=\"false\" style=\"display: inline;\" data-source=\"{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;in&quot;,&quot;1&quot;:&quot;at&quot;,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;on&quot;}\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">on</span>&nbsp;the&nbsp;<span class=\"editable editable-click editable-unsaved\" data-type=\"text\" data-emptytext=\"[road/landmark/business/building]\" data-value=\"Princes Freeway\" contenteditable=\"false\" style=\"display: inline;\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">Princes Freeway</span>&nbsp;between Darnum and Yarragon as a result of a road incident.</li></ul></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 120%; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom:20px\">There is currently no threat to\nthe community, but you should continue to stay informed and monitor conditions. </div><div style=\"margin-bottom:20px\"><b>What you should do:</b><div><ul><li>Keep the roads clear so emergency services can respond.</li><li>Follow the direction of emergency services.</li></ul></div></div><div style=\"margin-bottom:20px\"><div><b>Impacts in your area:</b></div><div><ul><li>The following road is closed: Princes Freeway, eastbound lanes between Darnum and Yarragon.</li><li>Emergency services will remain in the area.</li></ul></div></div><div style=\"margin-bottom:20px\">This message was issued\nby <span title=\"warning_issuing_agency\" class=\"param\" contenteditable=\"false\">Country Fire Authority</span>.&nbsp;<div><br></div><div><b>The next update is expected by </b><span title=\"warning_next_update\" class=\"param\" contenteditable=\"false\">20/06/2026 04:00 pm</span><b>&nbsp;or as the situation changes.&nbsp;</b></div><div><br></div><div><div><b>Use multiple sources to stay informed:</b>&nbsp;</div></div><div><ul><li><a href=\"http://emergency.vic.gov.au/respond/\" title=\"www.emergency.vic.gov.au\" target=\"_blank\">www.emergency.vic.gov.au</a></li><li><a href=\"https://vicemergency.zendesk.com/hc/en-gb/articles/115001055007-What-is-the-VicEmergency-Hotline-\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: white;\">VicEmergency Hotline</a>&nbsp;- freecall 1800 226\n226</li><li><a href=\"https://vicemergency.zendesk.com/hc/en-gb/articles/230492607-What-is-the-VicEmergency-app-\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\">VicEmergency app</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vicemergency\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\"> Facebook</a> or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/vicemergency\" title=\"Twitter\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a>&nbsp;(#vichazmat)</li><li>Tune in to ABC Local Radio, commercial and designated community radio stations, or Sky News TV.</li></ul><div><b>Accessibility:</b></div></div><div>The following services can\nhelp you, or someone you know, access information during an emergency. </div><div><ul><li>To access this information in other languages call the <a href=\"https://www.tisnational.gov.au/\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\">Translating\nand Interpreting Service</a>&nbsp;on&nbsp;131\n450&nbsp;(freecall) and ask them to call VicEmergency Hotline.</li><li>If you are deaf, hard of\nhearing, or have a speech/communication impairment contact the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.infrastructure.gov.au/media-communications-arts/phone/services-people-disability/accesshub/national-relay-service\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\">National\nRelay Service</a>&nbsp;and ask them to call the VicEmergency Hotline. </li></ul></div></div>","text":"ADVICE - CHEMICAL HAZARD - Stay Informed\nIncident Location: Princes Freeway, Darnum\nIssue Date: Saturday 20 June 2026, 09:57 am\nNext Update: Saturday 20 June 2026, 04:00 pm\n\nMore details at http://emergency.vic.gov.au/respond/#!/warning/42010/moreinfo\n\nThis Advice message is being issued for Darnum. \n- There are hazardous fumes on the Princes Freeway between Darnum and Yarragon as a result of a road incident.\n\n\nThere is currently no threat to the community, but you should continue to stay informed and monitor conditions. \n\n","sizeFmt":null,"incidentFeatures":[{"properties":{"feedType":"incident","sourceOrg":"EMV","sourceId":"42010","sourceFeed":"cop-cap","sourceTitle":"Advice","id":"42010","category1":"CBRNE","category2":"Chemical Hazard","name":"Advice","location":"Princes Freeway, Darnum","